English: SVG image of a Rubik's Cube. partially white
This shows a pristine Rubik's Cube. If you just need a general-purpose ordinary photo of one with the squares in all different places, use the image Rubiks cube scrambled.jpg. For a SVG of the same thing, see Rubiks cube scrambled.svg.
For a cube turned 1/4 turn up from this pristine cube image, see Back, Down, Front, Left, Right, Up
